<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201106/d723d54a273147fd99a96dba0f2def3c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>352，三下五除二搞定空气问题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>红点设计奖、医院、画室都在用</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">352源自成语<strong>“三下五除二”</strong>，<strong>意喻迅速快捷、干净利落解决空气污染问题。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/6cd38ed35a53435f81bd036b70639729.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
